## VR1 — Salary Range Check (Job__c)

**Purpose:** Ensure Max Salary >= Min Salary.

**Formula:**
```
AND(
    NOT(ISBLANK(Min_Salary__c)),
    NOT(ISBLANK(Max_Salary__c)),
    Max_Salary__c < Min_Salary__c
)
```
**Error Message:** `Maximum Salary must be greater than or equal to Minimum Salary.`

